9.7071L9.7071 15.7071C9.31658 16.0976 8.68341 16.0976 8.29289 15.7071C7.90236 15.3166 7.90236 14.6834 8.29289 14.2929L14.2929 8.29289C14.6834 7.90236 15.3166 7.90236 15.7071 8.29289ZM6.7071 9.29289C7.09763 9.68341 7.09763 10.3166 6.7071 10.7071L5.7071 11.7071C3.88849 13.5257 3.88849 16.4743 5.7071 18.2929C7.52572 20.1115 10.4743 20.1115 12.2929 18.2929L13.2929 17.2929C13.6834 16.9024 14.3166 16.9024 14.7071 17.2929C15.0976 17.6834 15.0976 18.3166 14.7071 18.7071L13.7071 19.7071C11.1074 22.3068 6.89255 22.3068 4.29289 19.7071C1.69322 17.1074 1.69322 12.8926 4.29289 10.2929L5.29289 9.29289C5.68341 8.90236 6.31658 8.90236 6.7071 9.29289Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></h2></div><div class="endpoint"><div class="section-left"><div class="docs-markdown-content"><p>Sent by the server when an Item is added to the default Conversation. This can happen in several cases:</p>
<ul>
<li>When the client sends a <code>conversation.item.create</code> event.</li>
<li>When the input audio buffer is committed. In this case the item will be a user message containing the audio from the buffer.</li>
<li>When the model is generating a Response. In this case the <code>conversation.item.added</code> event will be sent when the model starts generating a specific Item, and thus it will not yet have any content (and <code>status</code> will be <code>in_progress</code>).</li>
</ul>
<p>The event will include the full content of the Item (except when model is generating a Response) except for audio data, which can be retrieved separately with a <code>conversation.item.retrieve</code> event if necessary.</p></div><div class="param-table" id="realtime_server_events-conversation-item-added__table"><div class="param-row" id="realtime_server_events-conversation-item-added-event_id" data-normalized-id="realtime-server-events-conversation-item-added-event-id"><div class="param-row-header api-ref-anchor-link-hover"><a href="#realtime_server_events-conversation-item-added-event_id" data-anchor="realtime_server_events-conversation-item-added-event_id" id="realtime_server_events-conversation-item-added-event_id-anchor" data-normalized-id="realtime-server-events-conversation-item-added-event-id-anchor" class="api-ref-anchor-link"><svg width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.2929 5.7071C16.4743 3.88849 13.5257 3.88849 11.7071 5.7071L10.7071 6.7071C10.3166 7.09763 9.68341 7.09763 9.29289 6.7071C8.90236 6.31658 8.90236 5.68341 9.29289 5.29289L10.2929 4.29289C12.8926 1.69322 17.1074 1.69322 19.7071 4.29289C22.3068 6.89255 22.3068 11.1074 19.7071 13.7071L18.7071 14.7071C18.3166 15.0976 17.6834 15.0976 17.2929 14.7071C16.9024 14.3166 16.9024 13.6834 17.2929 13.2929L18.2929 12.2929C20.1115 10.4743 20.1115 7.52572 18.2929 5.7071ZM15.7071 8.29289C16.0976 8.68341 16.0976 9.31658 15.7071 9.7071L9.7071 15.7071C9.31658 16.0976 8.68341 16.0976 8.29289 15.7071C7.90236 15.3166 7.90236 14.6834 8.29289 14.2929L14.2929 8.29289C14.6834 7.90236 15.3166 7.90236 15.7071 8.29289ZM6.7071 9.29289C7.09763 9.68341 7.09763 10.3166 6.7071 10.7071L5.7071 11.7071C3.88849 13.5257 3.88849 16.4743 5.7071 18.2929C7.52572 20.1115 10.4743 20.1115 12.2929 18.2929L13.2929 17.2929C13.6834 16.9024 14.3166 16.9024 14.7071 17.2929C15.0976 17.6834 15.0976 18.3166 14.7071 18.7071L13.7071 19.7071C11.1074 22.3068 6.89255 22.3068 4.29289 19.7071C1.69322 17.1074 1.6932